On another note what graphics programs do you use to make your stuff? That Orion with a moving star field was sweet. I would have never thought of using 2 star fields moving at different rates to create the illusion of parallax. I saw some of the nit-picks such as the 'pulsing should last longer' and I just had to sit back and laugh.  I know that you must have 30 to 40 frames there already (that’s alot of work!) and at  4K-5K per frame a longer animation would take modem users what they would consider to be an excruciatingly long time to download. In that case you would get a &quot;can't you make it load faster whine. I think the animation is kick ass and professional the way it is. great work man.<br>
